---
title: Shrimp and Salmon Fusilli with Sweet Peppers
description: It’s hard not to love fusilli! We're keeping things easy-going with a simple tomato sauce, but bringing serious flavours with Italian spices, sweet peppers, juicy shrimp and tender salmon. This pasta is sure to become a family favourite!
